{"id":14,"date":"2025-09-05T16:52:02","date_gmt":"2025-09-05T16:52:02","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?page_id=14"},"modified":"2025-09-06T06:47:09","modified_gmt":"2025-09-06T06:47:09","slug":"portfolio","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/index.php\/portfolio\/","title":{"rendered":"Portfolio"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<style>\n\/* ==== General Styling ==== *\/\n.section-title {\n  font-size: 26px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  margin: 40px 0 20px;\n  color: #0073aa;\n  text-align: left;\n}\n\n.projects-container {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));\n  gap: 2rem;\n  padding: 10px;\n  font-family: \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n}\n\n.project-card {\n  background: #fff;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n  overflow: hidden;\n  transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n}\n.project-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-5px);\n}\n\n.project-header {\n  background: #0073aa;\n  color: #fff;\n  padding: 12px 16px;\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.project-body {\n  padding: 16px;\n}\n\n.project-body p {\n  font-size: 15px;\n  line-height: 1.5;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n}\n\n.project-links a {\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin-right: 10px;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  background: #0073aa;\n  color: #fff;\n  padding: 6px 12px;\n  border-radius: 6px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  transition: background 0.3s;\n}\n.project-links a:hover {\n  background: #005f8d;\n}\n\n\/* ==== Image Gallery ==== *\/\n.gallery {\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n}\n.gallery img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n  display: none;\n  object-fit: cover;\n}\n.gallery img.active {\n  display: block;\n  animation: fade 1s ease-in-out;\n}\n@keyframes fade {\n  from { opacity: 0.3; }\n  to { opacity: 1; }\n}\n\n\/* ==== Video Embed ==== *\/\n.video-container {\n  position: relative;\n  padding-bottom: 56.25%;\n  height: 0;\n  margin-top: 12px;\n}\n.video-container iframe {\n  position: absolute;\n  top:0;\n  left:0;\n  width:100%;\n  height:100%;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\n<!-- ================== PROJECTS ================== -->\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Projects<\/h2>\n<div class=\"projects-container\">\n\n  <!-- Tailstock Tool Holder -->\n  <div class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"project-header\">Tailstock Die Tool Holder<\/div>\n    <div class=\"project-body\">\n      <div class=\"gallery\" id=\"gallery-tailstock\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631493.jpg\" class=\"active\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631510.jpg\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631480.jpg\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631444.jpg\">\n      <\/div>\n      <p>Designed and manufactured an ergonomic tailstock die tool holder using <b>SolidWorks CAD modeling<\/b> and <b>lathe machining<\/b>. The tool holder improves operator comfort and enhances die threading precision during machining.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"project-links\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1pXTrq3WtxePYmgT3U3wV0EFVgUJbA0YM\/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">Details<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <!-- Vacuum Cleaner Car -->\n  <div class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"project-header\">Smart Bluetooth Vacuum Cleaner Car<\/div>\n    <div class=\"project-body\">\n      <div class=\"gallery\" id=\"gallery-vacuum\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631190.jpg\" class=\"active\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-113852.png\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-113955.png\">\n      <\/div>\n      <p>Built a <b>Bluetooth-controlled cleaning car<\/b> powered by an <b>Arduino Uno<\/b> and <b>CPU fans<\/b> to suck dust and small particles. The system was integrated with a smartphone app for wireless control, showcasing the potential of IoT in small-scale automation.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"project-links\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1NfPQ5zFFHCKDYhLe72kEoMUkZNJ7CpZm\/view\" target=\"_blank\">Details<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <!-- Fish Detection App -->\n  <div class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"project-header\">BD Freshwater Fish Detection App<\/div>\n    <div class=\"project-body\">\n      <div class=\"gallery\" id=\"gallery-fish\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/project.png\" class=\"active\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-114817.png\">\n      <\/div>\n      <p>Developed a <b>Vision Transformer (ViT) model<\/b> to classify 12 Bangladeshi freshwater fish species. The model was deployed in a <b>Streamlit web app<\/b> that provides real-time classification, supporting biodiversity research and aquaculture management.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"project-links\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/marufmullah50\/Fish-detection-app\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"video-container\">\n        <iframe src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/1uFwmIotmZg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <!-- Background Editor -->\n  <div class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"project-header\">Photo Background Editor App<\/div>\n    <div class=\"project-body\">\n      <div class=\"gallery\" id=\"gallery-bg\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/app-interface.png\" class=\"active\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-120029.png\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/photo.png\">\n      <\/div>\n      <p>Created a <b>Streamlit application<\/b> using <b>U\u00b2-Net ONNX<\/b> for background removal. Users can upload photos, remove or replace backgrounds, and download the edited results. Features include <b>Pillow-based editing<\/b> and support for transparent or custom-colored backgrounds.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"project-links\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/marufmullah50\/Photo-background-editor-Streamlit-App\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"video-container\">\n        <iframe src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Fegs76ylu-k\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- ================== THESIS ================== -->\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Thesis<\/h2>\n<div class=\"projects-container\">\n  <div class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"project-header\">Undergraduate Thesis: Densification of Natural Wood<\/div>\n    <div class=\"project-body\">\n      <div class=\"gallery\" id=\"gallery-thesis\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631162-scaled.jpg\" class=\"active\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-121135.png\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1757049631244.jpg\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/WhatsApp-Image-2025-09-06-at-12.05.37_ec58964a.jpg\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-122452.png\">\n        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-06-122513.png\">\n      <\/div>\n      <p>Conducted research on <b>densification of natural wood<\/b> to enhance its <b>mechanical and structural properties<\/b>. The study involved experimental analysis of moisture behavior, strength improvements, and potential applications in sustainable construction.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"project-links\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1vpVZQZMdddl-lyYXsE03T3hKZWrSqqi2\/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">Full Thesis<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- ================== PUBLICATIONS ================== -->\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Publications<\/h2>\n<div class=\"projects-container\">\n  <div class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"project-header\">Conference Paper<\/div>\n    <div class=\"project-body\">\n      <p><b>Impact Strength and Moisture Behaviour of Natural, Densified and Seasoned Wood: An Experimental Study.<\/b><br>\n      Co-authored with <b>Anika Tahsin, Md. Jamil Ahmed, Md. Anisur Rahman<\/b>.  \n      Accepted at the <b>3rd International Conference on Mechanical Engineering and Applied Sciences (ICMEAS), 2025<\/b>.<\/p>\n      <div class=\"project-links\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/18LPhozjqo-WKTq83NEwYE-vnDuJbnRpy\/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">View Paper<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\n\/\/ Auto slideshow for each gallery\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.gallery').forEach(gallery => {\n  let images = gallery.querySelectorAll('img');\n  let index = 0;\n  setInterval(() => {\n    images[index].classList.remove('active');\n    index = (index + 1) % images.length;\n    images[index].classList.add('active');\n  }, 3000); \/\/ change every 3s\n});\n<\/script>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Projects Tailstock Die Tool Holder 